Feature: Compatibility with different operating systems on mobile devices

	As a user
	I want to the application to be compatible with most versions of operating systems, be it 	Android and IOS
	So that I may have no problems in its use

Acceptance criteria:
	*The user can have an android or IOS system
	
	Scenario: The user wants to download the app
	 Given that the user has an Android or IOS device
	 And the user locates our application in the Play Store or App Store
	 When she the user tries to download the app on any of those operating systems
	 Then the app will download and function correctly despite de operating system
